Package me.amgelo563.javadocsgen.annotations

Annotation Type TestAnnotation

@Deprecated
@Target({TYPE,METHOD,FIELD})
@Retention(RUNTIME)
public @interface TestAnnotation
Deprecated.
This annotation is deprecated for testing.
This annotation is used to test all Javadoc scraping features for annotations.

It includes elements with defaults, multiple targets, retention policies, and deprecation for testing coverage.
